race.description: Mildura & District Real Estate Mdn Plate
race.comment: PALTINIAN (3) has been solid in two runs back, finishing fifth on each occasion. He was big odds in town at Sandown Hillside last time but ran admirably to only be beaten four lengths. Sets up well here back to easier company and should go close. MISS SOLAR HART (7) has had plenty of chances but is going okay, probably unsuited coming back in trip at Donald last time out. The run prior over this route has her in the mix. FOX CHARM (6) struggled out to 2100m at Echuca last time out which is a query but she'd been going well prior and can only be better for that run. Sets up well with Meech from the low gate. YOUBEEFORTY (5) ran a better race for second last time out and can sneak into the finish with natural improvement. MIGHTY MAC (2) is a rough hope up in trip.
